      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "This page is to summarize the dependencies of SAIL SW"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Compiler"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Qualcomm has developed their CDD and MCAL with 6.16.2 Fusa Arm compiler"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "So we may go with Arm compiler for SAIL, not the GHS"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We have the 6.16.2 FuSa compiler in W3 FSI project"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "How to get license for Arm FuSa compile"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "RequestMembershipARM-UBL…"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "OS"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Vector delivery uses Safe RTOS."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "But in the delivery to Bosch there is no Safe RTOS"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "But we have RTA-OS which is developed for SAIL in QAM8775"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
